00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:04.230
Welcome my friend to today's
lecture on international banking.

00:00:04.770 --> 00:00:10.230
Let's decode this concept like
detectives concept, explanation.

00:00:11.460 --> 00:00:13.200
So what is this big shot?

00:00:13.230 --> 00:00:14.370
International banking all about.

00:00:16.035 --> 00:00:20.475
It's just banking that has packed
its bags and gone on a world tour.

00:00:21.045 --> 00:00:25.515
It refers to all banking activities
that cross national borders.

00:00:26.025 --> 00:00:30.075
We are talking about financial
transactions and services provided

00:00:30.075 --> 00:00:34.845
by banks to individuals, businesses,
and even entire governments

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:36.200
across different countries.

00:00:37.035 --> 00:00:41.865
It's what facilitates international
trade, manages all that foreign exchange

00:00:41.865 --> 00:00:47.145
drama handles cross-border investments
and juggles the financial risks that

00:00:47.145 --> 00:00:49.275
come with play on a global field.

00:00:49.845 --> 00:00:54.315
Honestly, it's absolutely essential
for our globally interconnected

00:00:54.315 --> 00:00:59.235
economy, ensuring the smooth flow
of capital and commerce worldwide.

00:01:00.225 --> 00:01:01.665
Real world relevance.

00:01:02.715 --> 00:01:04.635
And why should you care about this?

00:01:04.635 --> 00:01:05.205
You ask.

00:01:05.475 --> 00:01:10.155
Simple understanding international
banking helps you become a star

00:01:10.185 --> 00:01:14.625
in client advisory, giving advice
on foreign trade finance and

00:01:14.655 --> 00:01:16.875
international investment opportunities.

00:01:17.355 --> 00:01:21.945
It's also crucial for currency
management that is managing foreign

00:01:21.945 --> 00:01:26.385
currency transactions and mitigating
those pesky exchange rate risks.

00:01:26.885 --> 00:01:31.745
Furthermore, it allows for sharp
economic analysis helping you assess

00:01:31.745 --> 00:01:36.695
global economic trends that impact
bank operations and client portfolios.

00:01:37.265 --> 00:01:39.965
And we cannot forget global compliance.

00:01:40.325 --> 00:01:44.885
It's all about navigating the complex
maze of international regulations

00:01:45.035 --> 00:01:49.385
and compliance requirements,
