the core definition and the

00:04:09.585 --> 00:04:11.145
why behind each concept.

00:04:11.505 --> 00:04:16.305
Second, for acronyms like Swift or
IMF, you must know the full form.

00:04:16.725 --> 00:04:20.954
Third, practice role identification
for any organization.

00:04:21.135 --> 00:04:24.170
Identify its primary role
in the financial system.

00:04:24.625 --> 00:04:27.745
Fourth, get good at
distinction and comparison.

00:04:28.075 --> 00:04:33.115
Understand the subtle differences between
similar terms like nostri versus vostro.

00:04:33.385 --> 00:04:36.115
