00:05:32.325 --> 00:05:33.435
The common traps.

00:05:33.645 --> 00:05:34.665
Let's avoid them.

00:05:34.995 --> 00:05:38.715
A classic mistake is confusing
the IMF and the World Bank.

00:05:39.105 --> 00:05:43.155
Remember, the IMF focuses on
global monetary cooperation

00:05:43.185 --> 00:05:44.655
and financial stability.

00:05:44.955 --> 00:05:49.035
The World Bank focuses on poverty
reduction and development assistance.

00:05:49.545 --> 00:05:52.725
Another big one is mixing
up nostri and vostro.

00:05:53.025 --> 00:05:56.835
Remember the mantra, nostri
is our bank's account abroad.

00:05:57.015 --> 00:05:59.535
Vostro is their bank's account with us.

00:05:59.945 --> 00:06:02.585
Also don't make the mistake of thinking.

00:06:02.765 --> 00:06:04.145
L-I-B-O-R is still primary.

00:06:04.445 --> 00:06:08.345
It has been largely phased out
for rates like SOR and Sonia.

00:06:08.765 --> 00:06:13.565
Many also ignored the basal accords,
but their principles influence banking

00:06:13.565 --> 00:06:16.355
regulations globally affecting all banks.

00:06:16.775 --> 00:06:19.745
Lastly, don't overlook
correspondent banking.

00:06:19.925 --> 00:06:22.595
It's fundamental for
cross-border transactions.

